<paragraph blockId="64.[151,616,1485,1512]" box="[151,616,1485,1512]" pageId="64" pageNumber="65">
<heading bold="true" box="[151,616,1485,1512]" fontSize="11" level="1" pageId="64" pageNumber="65" reason="1">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,616,1485,1512]" pageId="64" pageNumber="65">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Humala" authorityYear="2019" box="[151,437,1485,1512]" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Orthocentrus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="64" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ungularis">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,437,1485,1512]" italics="true" pageId="64" pageNumber="65">Orthocentrus ungularis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species-group
</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="64.[151,1437,1556,1727]" pageId="64" pageNumber="65">
This group characterised by the elongate body, long slender antenna with 27–35 flagellomeres, basal flagellomere 1.8–4.5 × as long as wide; posterior transverse carina of propodeum present between lateral longitudinal carinae, hind claws enlarged and areolet in fore wing wide pentagonal or open. There are known six species in 
<collectingCountry box="[1308,1398,1629,1655]" name="Mexico" pageId="64" pageNumber="65">Mexico</collectingCountry>
: 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="64" pageNumber="65">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Humala" authorityYear="2019" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Orthocentrus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="64" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="elongatus">O. elongatus</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Humala" authorityYear="2019" box="[276,466,1665,1691]" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Orthocentrus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="64" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flavoorbitalis">O. flavoorbitalis</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Humala" authorityYear="2019" box="[479,659,1665,1691]" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Orthocentrus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="64" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hidalgoensis">O. hidalgoensis</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Humala" authorityYear="2019" box="[672,844,1665,1691]" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Orthocentrus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="64" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longiventris">O. longiventris</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Humala" authorityYear="2019" box="[857,1004,1665,1691]" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Orthocentrus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="64" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rhombifer">O. rhombifer</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
and 
<emphasis box="[1063,1214,1665,1691]" italics="true" pageId="64" pageNumber="65">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Humala" authorityYear="2019" box="[1063,1210,1665,1691]" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Orthocentrus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="64" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ungularis">O. ungularis</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
This species-group was not reported from outside 
<collectingCountry box="[494,583,1701,1727]" name="Mexico" pageId="64" pageNumber="65">Mexico</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
